gil","lang_name":"Gilbertese"},{"language":"ms","lang_name":"Malay"},{"language":"lut","lang_name":"Lushootseed"}]},{"phelps":"BH11209","text":"Gee Kayne dah mah zon, Ke shay Manito, che ke kayne ne me nan, Shegwah che mah wim we to nan, Che mean e ge e ze yan. Che ke kayne ne me nan ke kaye da ma zon ke zong e ze win she quah neen aye pee chee nay. sou e ze yan, shegwa ka a pe chee we note e ze yun. She gwah neen apee chee ke tee mak e ze anne. Keen aye ta go ka Manito win, ka we che tas so win, Apee saig e ze an, kah ke kay kah ah ya yin.\n\n* I bear witness, O my God, that Thou hast created me to know Thee and to worship Thee. I testify, at this moment, to my powerlessness and to Thy might, to my poverty and to Thy wealth.\nThere is none other God but Thee, the Help in Peril, the Self-Subsisting.","name":"Short Obligatory Prayer","source":"bahaiprayers.net","version":"58a866f9-f971-4322-8161-25a628eab906","book_cats":{"af":{"cat":"Kort verpligte gebed","order_in_cat":1},"am":{"cat":"አጭሩ (Short)","order_in_cat":1},"ar":{"cat":"الصلاة   الصغيرة","order_in_cat":1},"az":{"cat":"Qısa Namaz","order_in_cat":1},"be":{"cat":"Кароткая абавязковая малітва","order_in_cat":1},"bg":{"cat":"Кратка задължителна молитва","order_in_cat":1},"ca":{"cat":"Oració obligatòria curta","order_in_cat":1},"cs":{"cat":"Krátká denní modlitba","order_in_cat":1},"da":{"cat":"Kort Obligatorisk Bøn","order_in_cat":1},"de":{"cat":"Das kurze Pflichtgebet","order_in_cat":1},"en":{"cat":"Short Obligatory Prayer","order_in_cat":1},"es":{"cat":"Oración obligatoria corta","order_in_cat":1},"fa":{"cat":"نماز صغیر","order_in_cat":1},"fi":{"cat":"Lyhyt velvollisuusrukous","order_in_cat":1},"fr":{"cat":"Prières prescrites","order_in_cat":1},"ha":{"cat":"Sallar Farilla Gajera","order_in_cat":1},"hi":{"cat":"मध्यम अनिवार्य प्रार्थना","order_in_cat":1},"hu":{"cat":"Rövid kötelező ima","order_in_cat":1},"is":{"cat":"Stutta skyldubænin","order_in_cat":1},"it":{"cat":"Preghiera Obbligatoria Breve","order_in_cat":